2 ffd fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">时，<span class="_ _5"></span>常会深深感觉到，<span class="_ _5"></span>不管是讲哪一个领域的知识，<span class="_ _5"></span>实际上</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y43 ffd fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">在佛教中都能找得到，<span class="_ _8"></span>这些知识并不太新鲜。<span class="_ _8"></span>我有时候在书</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y44 ffd fs3 fc0 sc0 ls40 ws0">店看到一些畅销书，比如《当下的力量》<span class="_ _b"></span><span class="ls0">、<span class="_ _b"></span><span class="ls48">《秘密》<span class="_ _1d"></span><span class="ls52">，翻开以</span></span></span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y46 ffd fs3 fc0 sc0 ls21 ws0">后，<span class="_ _5"></span>发现这些所表达的都不离大乘佛教的教义。<span class="_ _5"></span>当然，<span class="_ _5"></span>也可</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y47 ffd fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">能是我对世间比较孤陋寡闻，<span class="_ _8"></span>但至今为止，<span class="_ _8"></span>我所接触的包罗</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yf2 ffd fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">万象的各种知识，确实都可以摄集在佛教的理念中。 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
